data: {"event_data":"{\"message\":{\"content_type\":2008,\"content\":\"{}\",\"meta_infos\":[{\"type\":-4,\"info\":\"{\\\"insert_text\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.who.int/china/health-topics/air-pollution/2?adlt=strict\\\",\\\"icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"website_name\\\":\\\"who.int\\\",\\\"pos\\\":[977],\\\"type\\\":4,\\\"summary\\\":\\\"air pollution \\\\n air pollution in china \\\\n air pollution leads people to be exposed to fine particles in polluted air that penetrate deep into the lungs and cardiovascular system , causing diseases including stroke , heart disease , lung cancer , chronic obstructive pulmonary diseases and respiratory infections . industry , transportation , coal power plants and household solid fuel usage are major contributors to air pollution . though some progress has been made , air pollution remains at an alarming rate in china , and affects economies and people ’s quality of life . \\\\n air pollution is responsible for about 2 million deaths in china per year . of those deaths , ambient air pollution alone caused more than 1 million deaths , while household air pollution from cooking with polluting fuels and technologies caused another million deaths in the same period in china . \\\\n technical links \\\\n fact sheets \\\\n household air pollution \\\\n ambient ( outdoor ) air pollution \\\\n data \\\\n sdg target 3.9 | mortality from environmental pollution \\\\n sdg target 11.6 | clean cities \\\\n sdg target 7.1 | clean household energy \\\\n who resolutions \\\\n health and the environment , draft road map for an enhanced global response to the adverse health effects of air pollution , report by the secretariat ( a 69 / 18 ) \\\\n statement by the world meteorological organization ( wpr / rc 65 / igo / 3 ) \\\\n environmental health ( wpr / rc 67 . r 2 ) \\\\n who / y . shimizu \\\\n © credits \\\\n did you know ? \\\\n the western pacific region bears the most share of death from air pollution . \\\\n every 14 seconds \\\\n a person dies from air pollution in the western pacific region . \\\\n multimedia\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Air pollution\\\",\\\"pos_rune\\\":[977],\\\"tag_title\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"search_empty\\\":0,\\\"start_index\\\":660}\"}]},\"message_id\":\"1872843662282754\",\"local_message_id\":\"14da4f40-003a-11f0-af0f-47db3297321d\",\"conversation_id\":\"1878382324998146\",\"local_conversation_id\":\"local_2092319364225109\",\"section_id\":\"1878382324998402\",\"reply_id\":\"1872843662282498\",\"is_delta\":true,\"status\":4,\"input_content_type\":2001,\"message_index\":2,\"bot_id\":\"7338286299411103781\"}","event_id":"37","event_type":2001}

